---
layout: base.njk
permalink: /blog/index.html
title: Articles
description: Articles de fond sur l'entraînement, l'hypertrophie et la force — écrits par les coachs Relentless Strength Systems.
extraCss: |
  /* ─── BLOG INDEX ─── */
  .blog-hero {
    background: var(--dark);
    padding: 5rem 2rem 4rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .section-tag {
    font-family: var(--font-cond);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .blog-hero h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .blog-hero p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    max-width: 600px;
  }
  .blog-main {
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    min-height: 50vh;
  }
  .articles-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .article-card {
    background: var(--dark2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 1.8rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .article-card:hover { border-color: rgba(200,16,46,0.35); }
  .article-date {
    font-family: var(--font-cond);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .article-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.1;
  }
  .article-excerpt {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
    flex: 1;
  }
  .article-author {
    font-family: var(--font-cond);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .article-arrow {
    font-family: var(--font-cond);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
  }
  .empty-state {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) { .articles-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr); } }
  @media (max-width: 600px) { .articles-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
---

<section class="blog-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-tag">Contenu éducatif</p>
    <h1>ARTICLES</h1>
    <p>Des articles de fond sur l'entraînement, l'hypertrophie et la force — écrits par nos coachs.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="blog-main">
  {% if collections.posts.length %}
    <div class="articles-grid">
      {% for post in collections.posts %}
      <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="article-card">
        <div class="article-date">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</div>
        <div class="article-title">{{ post.data.title | upper }}</div>
        {% if post.data.excerpt %}
        <div class="article-excerpt">{{ post.data.excerpt }}</div>
        {% endif %}
        {% if post.data.author %}
        <div class="article-author">Par {{ post.data.author }}</div>
        {% endif %}
        <span class="article-arrow">Lire l'article →</span>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  {% else %}
    <div class="empty-state">Aucun article publié pour l'instant.</div>
  {% endif %}
</section>
